Multi-Threaded Shearsort Algorithm C++
--------------------------------------
AUTHOR
    Allen Bradley Roberts

NAME
    shearsort - Runs the shearsort algorithm on a 2D square matrix which is defined in a file labeled "input.txt"

MAKE
    type "make" in the terminal to create the ./shearsort program.
    type "make clean" in the terminal to remove old builds of ./shearsort

RUN
    ./shearsort 
        This is all that is needed to run Shearsort.
        Be sure to include the input.txt file with a square matrix.